text: John de Holcroft (fl. 1373–1383) was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Lancashire in 1373 and October 1383. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:English MPs 1373 Category:English MPs October 1383 Category:Members of the Parliament of England (pre-1707) for Lancashire
